    public enum XMLTags

    • Field Detail

      • OPEN_TAG_PATTERN

        public static final String OPEN_TAG_PATTERN
        pattern that matches for open tag for provided tag name. e.g.: String.format(OPEN_TAG_PATTERN, XMLTags.VARIABLES seeks for the string like this: <variables>, < variables>, <variables >, etc.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values

      • CLOSE_TAG_PATTERN

        public static final String CLOSE_TAG_PATTERN
        pattern that matches for open tag for provided tag name. e.g.: String.format(CLOSE_TAG_PATTERN, XMLTags.VARIABLES seeks for the string like this: </variables>, <variables/> </ variables>, < / variables >, etc.
        See Also:
        Constant Field Values
